			<h:tr>
				<h:td style="border:#e3e3e3 1px solid; background:#f2f6f9; padding:10px; font-size:12px;">To maintain your reputation as a sender it is important to have consent to send emails from every single subscriber in your list.
						A failure to follow these practices may result in termination of your account with us.</h:td>
			</h:tr>
		
		</h:table>
