						</h:tr>
						<h:tr>
							<h:td style="padding:0 0 30px 0; font-size:12px;">	If you told the card owner you would be in contact, you have consent.. If you did not suggest either with a sign or verbally that you would be contacting them, you do not have consent.</h:td>
						</h:tr>
						

